{"title":"乘积平均数","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":125,"url":"http://www.joyoi.cn/problem/codevs-1389","statement":[{"title":"","format":"html_final","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n题目描述\n<small>Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>定义 n 个数的乘积平均数为这 n 个数的乘积开 n 次方。<br>给定 n 个正整数，求它们的乘积平均数。</p>\n<p><span style=\"\">给定n 个正整数，求它们的乘积平均数。</span></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输入描述\n<small>Input Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>第一行，一个数 n<br>接下来一行 n 个数，表示给定的 n 个数</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输出描述\n<small>Output Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>一个实数，表示给定数的乘积平均数，保留2 位小数输出</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输入\n<small>Sample Input</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>2<br>2 8</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输出\n<small>Sample Output</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>4.00</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n数据范围及提示\n<small>Data Size & Hint</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>对于 100%的数据，n ≤ 100000，每个数均为正整数且不超过 10</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n"}]}